President Muhammadu Buhari has commiserated with elder statesman and former military Governor of Plateau State, Air Commodore Dan Suleiman over the death of his wife, Marie Dan Suleiman, who will be laid to rest at the weekend. He said that Mrs. Marie Dan Suleiman led an exemplary life worthy of emulation. she was a devoted Christian mother,grandmother, great grandmother and community leader. she will be fondly remembered for her philanthropic contributions to humanity,moral forthrightness, selfless service to her family and enormous contribution to her community. May the almighty comfort and give the entire family the fortitude to bear the loss. 